c: 6
v: 44
t: "Ke kaloku zathi zisakusilibala (isilumkiso) eso zazikhunjuzwe ngaso, Sazivulela amasango abo bonke (ubuncwane) bezinto, kwala xa ziphakathi naphakathi kolo lonwabo zazilunikiwe, Sasuka ngesaquphe Sazithabatha (ngesohlwayo) Yeha kuzo! Zagaxeleka entshabalalweni zinokuzisola okunzulu nosizi"